      "title": "IMF concludes mission",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The IMF mission concluded its staff mission yesterday after signing a staff-level agreement with the Sri Lankan government. The officials held a press conference in the morning to brief the media about the staff agreement and the way forward for Sri Lanka. Pix by Kithsiri de Mel"
